  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have made your pact with a mysterious entity from the Unformed Maze - a force that manifests in sentient magic weapons carved from the stuff of shadow. The mighty sword Blackrazor is the most notable of these weapons, which have been spread across the multiverse over the ages. The shadowy force behind these weapons can offer power to warlocks who form pacts with it. Many hexblade warlocks create weapons that emulate those formed in the Unformed Maze. Others forgo such arms, content to weave the dark magic of that plane into their spellcasting.</p><p>Because the Shepherd of Fate is known to have forged the first of these weapons by folding the broken threads of fate together, many sages speculate that she and the force are one and that the weapons, along with hexblade warlocks, are tools she uses to manipulate events on the Material Plane to her inscrutable ends.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
